---
title: Quick Korean Beef, Corn & Slaw Bowl with Sesame Aioli, Fried Egg & Peanuts
description: This sizzling hot Korean beef from the pan is a delight unparalleled. Delicious marinated beef and the joy of simplicity are winners
in this dish. A sprinkle of crushed peanuts are the crowning glory of this brilliant twist on the weeknight dinner.

